name: ABE
description: Hey, I’m Abe—America’s Official Bird. Abe's short for - American Bald Eagle. You've seen him on dollar bills, the SEC's logo, the President’s seal, and countless memes. Abe's not just America's #1 bird, he's the most famous bird in the history of the world. We all know America’s #1—so where do you think Abe’s heading? CACAAWWWW! tOkENOMICS - Abe dropped 350,000,000 tokens —one for every American and called it a day. No infinite money printer - this ain't one of Jerome Powell's wet dreams.
